data.description: Hartwell The phenomenal four-bedroom Hartwell at Stone Crest Estate is sure to be the talk of the town with its spacious, upgraded interiors and stunning exterior design. The Hartwell features four bedrooms, including a master suite, two and a half bathrooms, a study, formal dining area, a spacious family room and an open breakfast space. If you thought the perfect home for you didn't exist, come tour the Hartwell to see that it does!
